Furnish the Audit Team with advance copy of perfected contracts and POs together with the supporting documents and AIR for accepted deliveries in accordance with the requirements of COA Circular Nos. 2009-001 and 95-006, respectively.

We recommended and Management agreed to adhere to the relevant guidelines on the utilization of LDRRMF by observing, among others, the following:
Incorporate all identified disaster-related PPAs to be funded by the City Government in the AIP/SIP;
Ensure compliance with the documentary requirements for all disbursements chargeable against the LDRRMF;
Submit to the Audit Team a copy of report of inspection of consumable and perishable items within 24 hours from acceptance of the items and a copy of PO/contract within five working days from execution of the PO/contract;
